HELP SORT
  SORT <file> [fields...] BY <field> [BY-DSND ...]
  Formatting clauses (any position after verb/file):
    HEADING "text" — @DATE @TIME @PAGE @<n> substitution
    BREAK-ON <field>  TOTAL <field>  ID-SUPP
  Pagination: SET PAGE-LENGTH n | GET PAGE-LENGTH (when HEADING present)
  See docs/english-formatting.md and docs/english.md
